---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="404 - 访问受限 | Chemic.dev">
  <main class="min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-8xl md:text-9xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-cyan-400 drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(52,211,153,0.5)]">
        404
      </h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-200 tracking-wide">
          [ 警告 ] 区域未授权或已逸散
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm md:text-base max-w-md mx-auto mt-2">
          ERR_CONNECTION_REFUSED: 目标数据节点不存在。<br/>
          您正在尝试访问当前空间中未被定义的物理地址。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:bg-emerald-500/10 text-gray-300 hover:text-emerald-400 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 group font-mono">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
          </svg>
          返回主控台 (cd ~/)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>